  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/729640/extras/281821fa85612f43c454f74498f2ea19.poster.avif?t=1729016359\" width=680 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/729640/extras/281821fa85612f43c454f74498f2ea19.webm?t=1729016359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/729640/extras/281821fa85612f43c454f74498f2ea19.mp4?t=1729016359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>BOMBFEST</strong> is an award-winning party game for you and up to three friends! Battle in wooden forts, on folding chairs, and inside the kitchen sink as you attempt to be the last player standing. Use bombs to eliminate your foes, but don’t get caught in a chain reaction of explosions!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/729640/extras/a7a3793d10771f40d04341be385c0a0c.poster.avif?t=1729016359\" width=680 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/729640/extras/a7a3793d10771f40d04341be385c0a0c.webm?t=1729016359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/729640/extras/a7a3793d10771f40d04341be385c0a0c.mp4?t=1729016359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>4 player local multiplayer for friendly battles or settling grudges!<br></li><li>13 unique bombs for blowing away the competition!<br></li><li>14 hand-crafted stages for you to duke it out on!<br></li><li>Plenty of options and modifiers to customize your experience!<br></li><li>Unlock new bombs, stages, characters, and more as you play!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/729640/extras/7acd29b9bef641cd7aa99d0f71fd526e.poster.avif?t=1729016359\" width=680 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/729640/extras/7acd29b9bef641cd7aa99d0f71fd526e.webm?t=1729016359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/729640/extras/7acd29b9bef641cd7aa99d0f71fd526e.mp4?t=1729016359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>\"This game is amazing... [it's] a genuinely hilarious experience.\" - Jesse Cox, YouTube Personality",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/729640/extras/281821fa85612f43c454f74498f2ea19.poster.avif?t=1729016359\" width=680 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/729640/extras/281821fa85612f43c454f74498f2ea19.webm?t=1729016359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/729640/extras/281821fa85612f43c454f74498f2ea19.mp4?t=1729016359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>BOMBFEST</strong> is an award-winning party game for you and up to three friends! Battle in wooden forts, on folding chairs, and inside the kitchen sink as you attempt to be the last player standing. Use bombs to eliminate your foes, but don’t get caught in a chain reaction of explosions!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/729640/extras/a7a3793d10771f40d04341be385c0a0c.poster.avif?t=1729016359\" width=680 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/729640/extras/a7a3793d10771f40d04341be385c0a0c.webm?t=1729016359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/729640/extras/a7a3793d10771f40d04341be385c0a0c.mp4?t=1729016359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>4 player local multiplayer for friendly battles or settling grudges!<br></li><li>13 unique bombs for blowing away the competition!<br></li><li>14 hand-crafted stages for you to duke it out on!<br></li><li>Plenty of options and modifiers to customize your experience!<br></li><li>Unlock new bombs, stages, characters, and more as you play!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/729640/extras/7acd29b9bef641cd7aa99d0f71fd526e.poster.avif?t=1729016359\" width=680 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/729640/extras/7acd29b9bef641cd7aa99d0f71fd526e.webm?t=1729016359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/729640/extras/7acd29b9bef641cd7aa99d0f71fd526e.mp4?t=1729016359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>\"This game is amazing... [it's] a genuinely hilarious experience.\" - Jesse Cox, YouTube Personality",
